Dear Tamar, dear Adam,



We hope this email finds you both well and safe.



We wanted to provide you with an update on the Coller International Partner=
s VIII Private-Equity Backed Notes transaction (=E2=80=9CPBN=E2=80=9D). We =
are pleased to report that the underlying fund CIP VIII is currently tracki=
ng well. Please let us know if you would like to have a more detailed portf=
olio update.



Following the first close on 28 September 2020, we continued working on ups=
izing the transaction with investors who required more time to finalize the=
ir due diligence. We are pleased to inform that we are currently targeting =
a second close on the week commencing January 11, with certain first close =
investors wishing to upsize their existing investment alongside a number of=
 new investors who will participate in the second close. As mentioned in th=
e Additional Issuance Offering Memorandum that was previously shared with y=
ou, upsizing of the transaction will not affect the capital structure of th=
e transaction. Should you be interested in increasing your investment, we w=
ould be happy to provide you with a more detailed update on the transaction=
 and answer any of your questions.



Additionally, please note that the first distribution report for the transa=
ction will be released on the first payment date of 15 January 2021. Please=
 note that these reports can only be accessed through the BNYMellon investo=
r website. Please see below for details on how you can access the BNYMellon=
 investor website:

  1.  Investor reports can be accessed through the following website: https=
://gctinvestorreporting.bnymellon.com<https://clicktime.symantec.com/3GwsYQ=
ePrhaoN82obxrRKhW7Vc?u=3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Furldefense.com%2Fv3%2F__https%3A%2Fc=
licktime.symantec.com%2F3zUhL1LuWvwzv2KDmnkbrn7Vc%3Fu%3Dhttps%2A3A%2A2F%2A2=
Furldefense.com%2A2Fv3%2A2F__https%2A3A%2A2Fgctinvestorreporting.bnymellon.=
com__%2A3B%2A21%2A21JqX-yBvFPUQ%2A21xoz2AQNVHekLzeZ_3znQtOjfPqs0n7OVtZVEJWt=
sdVti95GCSJHbkQ-JVG_vefkN2w%2A24__%3BJSUlJSUlJSUlJSUl%21%21JqX-yBvFPUQ%21zJ=
oBaohkDtADZk_5emo5-3Zfc85pNKqK33betIijlXE0JHNUZCAV4AxfWo5zgMLdPg%24>
  2.  You will need to create a profile and attach the necessary exhibits p=
er the Indenture to provide proof of position ownership (i.e. copy of the c=
ertificated note or DTC screenshot)
  3.  Upon receipt of the request and validation by the BNYMellon team, you=
r access will be approved
  4.  Your main contact at BNYMellon will be Maritza Hernandez (please see =
below for her contact details). We kindly ask that you reach out to her dir=
ectly with your access request/any questions and please feel free to copy c=
cpbnexecution@collercapital.com<mailto:ccpbnexecution@collercapital.com>

